If they practice for disillusionment dispassion and cessation regarding form theyre qualified to be called a mendicant who practices in line with the teaching
If theyre freed by not grasping by disillusionment dispassion and cessation regarding form theyre qualified to be called a mendicant who has attained extinguishment in this very life
