If you take pleasure in suffering I say youre not exempt from suffering
If you take pleasure in feeling 
perception 
consciousness you take pleasure in suffering
If you take pleasure in suffering I say youre not exempt from suffering
If you dont take pleasure in form you dont take pleasure in suffering
If you dont take pleasure in suffering I say youre exempt from suffering
If you dont take pleasure in feeling 
perception 
consciousness you dont take pleasure in suffering
