who gives things up and doesnt grasp at them
who discards things and doesnt amass them
who dissipates things and doesnt get clouded by them
And what things do they get rid of and not accumulate
They get rid of form and dont accumulate it
consciousness and dont accumulate it
And what things do they give up and not grasp
They give up form and dont grasp it
consciousness and dont grasp it
And what things do they discard and not amass
They discard form and dont amass it
consciousness and dont amass it
