Similes
Rice Pots
At Sāvatthī
Mendicants suppose one person was to give a gift of a hundred pots of rice in the morning at midday and in the evening And someone else was to develop a heart of love even just as long as it takes to pull a cows udder The latter would be more fruitful
So you should train like this
We will develop the hearts release by love Well cultivate it make it our vehicle and our basis keep it up consolidate it and properly implement it
Thats how you should train
