Retreat
Mendicants meditate in retreat
A mendicant in retreat truly understands
What do they truly understand
They truly understand This is suffering  This is the origin of suffering  This is the cessation of suffering  This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering
Meditate in retreat
A mendicant in retreat truly understands
Thats why you should practice meditation to understand This is suffering  This is the origin of suffering  This is the cessation of suffering  This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering
