Linked Discourses
The Eye
The Eye
At Sāvatthī
Mendicants the eye is impermanent perishing and changing
and mind are impermanent perishing and changing
Someone who has faith and confidence in these principles is called a follower by faith Theyve arrived at inevitability regarding the right path theyve arrived at the level of the good person and theyve transcended the level of the bad person
They cant do any deed which would make them be reborn in hell the animal realm or the ghost realm
They cant die without realizing the fruit of streamentry
Someone who accepts these principles after considering them with a degree of wisdom is called a follower of the teachings Theyve arrived at inevitability regarding the right path theyve arrived at the level of the good person and theyve transcended the level of the bad person
They cant do any deed which would make them be reborn in hell the animal realm or the ghost realm
They cant die without realizing the fruit of streamentry
Someone who understands and sees these principles is called a streamenterer not liable to be reborn in the underworld bound for awakening
