Now is during seven days allowable with during a short period or is it not allowable
Now is during life allowable with during a short period or is it not allowable
Now is during seven days allowable with during a watch of the night or is it not allowable
Now is during life allowable with during a watch of the night or is it not allowable
Now is during life allowable with during seven days or is it not allowable
They told this matter to the Lord
He said Monks during a watch of the night with during a short period is allowable at the right time on the day it is accepted it is not allowable at the wrong time
Monks during seven days with during a short period is allowable at the right time on the day it is accepted it is not allowable at the wrong time
Monks during life with during a short period is allowable at the right time on the day it is accepted it is not allowable at the wrong time
Monks during seven days with during a watch of the night is allowable in a watch of the night on the day it is accepted it is not allowable after the watch of the night is ended
Monks during life with during a watch of the night is allowable in a watch of the night on the day it is accepted it is not allowable after the watch of the night is ended
Monks during life with during seven days is allowable for seven days it is not allowable after the seven days are ended
Then the Lord walking on tour in due course arrived at tumā
The Lord stayed there in tumā in the House with the threshingfloor
Then he who had gone forth when old having had a quantity of conjey prepared towards the end of that night brought it to the Lord saying Lord may the Lord accept conjey from me
Now Truthfinders ask knowing and knowing do not ask they ask knowing the right time  and they do not ask knowing the right time  Truthfinders ask about what belongs to the goal not about what does not belong to the goal there is bridgebreaking for Truthfinders in whatever does not belong to the goal Awakened ones Lords question monks concerning two matters either Shall we preach dhamma or Shall we lay down a rule of training for disciples
