that in a population obsessed by the stain of miserliness I dwell at home with a mind devoid of the stain of miserliness freely generous openhanded delighting in relinquishment devoted to charity delighting in giving and sharing
There exists in me too such faith as those deities possessed because of which when they passed away here they were reborn there
there exists in me too such virtuous behavior
there exists in me too such learning
there exists in me too such generosity
